    "claim": "`Solvency.getBorrowAmounts` calls `getRcomp` for every asset in `_allSiloAssets` before checking whether the user actually has any debt in that asset. Because `isSolvent` is used in withdrawal, post-borrow validation, and liquidation, one reverting or unavailable model on any synced or removed bridge asset can make those flows revert for everyone in the silo.",
